[
  {
    "start": 0.0,
    "end": 4.08,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "哈囉 各位衝 A 的會考戰士們",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0
  },
  {
    "start": 4.58,
    "end": 9.86,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "我是彥君老師 今天來到 第七十三集",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0
  },
  {
    "start": 10.36,
    "end": 13.36,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "大家好 我是曉臻助教",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0
  },
  {
    "start": 13.86,
    "end": 18.18,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "老師 今天要講 兩顆星的 回聲大魔王",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0
  },
  {
    "start": 18.68,
    "end": 24.25,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "沒錯 戰士們記得 回聲跟原本的聲音",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0
  },
  {
    "start": 24.75,
    "end": 29.09,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "只有 振幅跟方向 不同 其他都不會變",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0
  },
  {
    "start": 29.59,
    "end": 34.13,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "講義上說 至少要 十七公尺 才聽得到回聲",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0
  },
  {
    "start": 34.63,
    "end": 38.11,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "這個 十七公尺 是怎麼算出來的呀",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0
  },
  {
    "start": 38.61,
    "end": 42.86,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "人耳要分辨回聲 至少需要 零點一秒",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0
  },
  {
    "start": 43.36,
    "end": 47.58,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "聲音秒速 三百四十 乘以 零點一秒",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0
  },
  {
    "start": 48.08,
    "end": 51.94,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "代表聲音來回 總共走了 三十四公尺",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0
  },
  {
    "start": 52.44,
    "end": 56.31,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "除以二 單趟距離 就是十七公尺啦",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0
  },
  {
    "start": 56.81,
    "end": 9999.0,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "\\text{單趟} = \\frac{340m/s \\times 0.1s}{2} = 17m",
    "is_pinned": true,
    "pin_level": 1
  },
  {
    "start": 60.12,
    "end": 65.2,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "哇 來回除以二 這個推導真的太清楚了",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0
  },
  {
    "start": 65.7,
    "end": 70.0,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "接下來看 超聲波 頻率超過 兩萬赫茲",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0
  },
  {
    "start": 70.5,
    "end": 74.75,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "因為人類 聽不到 所以有很多 神奇應用喔",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0
  },
  {
    "start": 75.25,
    "end": 79.88,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "像是 判斷水深、 倒車雷達 還有超音波掃描",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0
  },
  {
    "start": 80.38,
    "end": 86.84,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "沒錯 還有蝙蝠飛行 洗眼鏡的 超音波清潔",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0
  },
  {
    "start": 87.34,
    "end": 91.54,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "老師 那如果想 避免回聲 干擾怎麼辦",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0
  },
  {
    "start": 92.04,
    "end": 97.58,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "很簡單 只要用 柔軟而且 不平整的材質",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0
  },
  {
    "start": 98.08,
    "end": 102.23,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "就能把聲音 吸收或打散 避免回聲囉",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0
  },
  {
    "start": 102.73,
    "end": 107.2,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "懂了 柔軟不平整 就能消滅回聲",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0
  },
  {
    "start": 107.7,
    "end": 112.11,
    "speaker": "彥君",
    "text": "觀念全通了 我是彥君老師",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0
  },
  {
    "start": 112.61,
    "end": 114.75,
    "speaker": "曉臻",
    "text": "我是曉臻助教",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0
  },
  {
    "start": 115.25,
    "end": 118.18,
    "speaker": "合聲",
    "text": "來回除二 柔軟吸音",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0
  },
  {
    "start": 118.68,
    "end": 122.01,
    "speaker": "合聲",
    "text": "戰士們 我們頂峰相見",
    "is_pinned": false,
    "pin_level": 0
  }
]